(I always just feel sad for the amature cooks, not that they cook so poorly, because that can be fixed, but that they actually think what they make -- premade gravy packets?!? -- actually tastes good!!!  Scary!  On the other hand this was engaging, and I really enjoyed seeing the chefs eating the food together.  So much more useful to see folks talking about how the final products taste.  Well done!!
